result.execSummary:
The defendant Edgar Serrano was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Edgar Serrano is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Edgar Serrano was found guilty of Disorderly Conduct, a class B misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 947.01(1).
